1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO ENACT THE NORTH CAROLINA DIGITAL ASSET AND STABLECOIN
3 ACT, AS RECOMMENDED BY THE HOUSE SELECT COMMITTEE ON
